message.body: No worries! We'll make it happen sooner or later. Tonight's no good for me but maybe later in the week.
Hey are you gonna be at the Pig Iron benefit tonight?
Hell yes! I'll see you there. Let's have that whisky we were deprived of!
Downstairs, right in the middle behind the chairs
Yo Kennedy! Bring yer ipod today an i'll bring dah money.
Bring it to the show! Thanks Kennedy. Also, is your ipod touch around there?? I think it fell out of my coat ._.
Argh. You're a-fucking-mazing. I owe you a drink.
That's so sweet of you. Don't worry about it, i'll just get it from you tonight! :)
Coolcool! I'll be home at 3:30 if that helps, if not I'll see ya tonight!
